column4: Nah son clear dope freaks me out

Got a new dope boy in a different town after being ripped off everytime the past week in my town, picked up 5 bags and now im down to 1 bag as you can see haha. the dope is pretty fire though, its also interesting. it gives a really good rush then a sedating high, and then you feel sober for a while and then out of nowhere you get a nod for a long time. never had dope like this ever before but i got it for a good price and it keeps me good and happy.

sorry for the bad picture quality i have a really shitty flip phone.
basically. its some lg phone with a slide out keyboard that doesnt have the function to focus when taking a pic.
its just the pic, in person its a amberish tint to the dope in the rig. you can kinda see it in the pic. look at the dope in the rig then look down at the rest of the rig you can see the difference
That's how fentanyl treats me. be careful.

Yeah it browns out usually you open. That said I had some off white stuff almost yellow. People thought it was shit. Turned out it was pretty damn pure. Got passed on because people thought it was crap and my shit dboy give me discount. If icicles a tiny amount in this shit had me drooling on my junk.

ive been being careful with it, it might have some fent cut because ive noticed some shots will last a whole 5 hours of feeling good and other shots will just last about 3 hours and youll be fiending for a redose. if it is fent cut its very weakly cut with fent which im fine with.
